    }
    writer {
      name: "Dalan Musson"
    }
    rating: "Bad"
    comments: "The concept is just a rehash of \"Captain America: The Winter Soldier,\" with a loophole sequel to \"The Incredible Hulk\"; the plot structure is very straightforward and linear; character writing is bad because none of these characters have depth; They try to make Ross this \"Trump-like\" character, but give him sympathy, and they try to introduce doubt about Sam Wilson as the new Captain America, but this was already addressed in the TV show and it doesn\'t really go anywhere in this movie"
  }
